disco (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Unified CLI with all management functionality
  * Automatic node discovery via UDP broadcast
  * Service detection and announcement
  * Native NSS integration for Linux
  * Optional DNS server for .disco domain
  * GPS time synchronization support
  * Message signing and verification
  * Comprehensive input validation
  * Security hardening (command injection prevention)
  * Test coverage at 57.4%

